<h3 id="what-is-honkit">What is HonKit?</h3>
<p><code>honkit</code> is a command line tool (and Node.js library) for building beautiful books using GitHub/Git and Markdown with <strong><a href="GLOSSARY.html#md-files" class="glossary-term" title="This is a test that the glossary term .MD files will parse as expected.">.MD files</a></strong> (or AsciiDoc). This documentation has been generated using <code>honkit</code>.</p>
